### Webhook Receiver Test Client

# Valid signature - should return 200
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
X-Webhook-Signature: e73d5219016ffe8ebb6eee3861c2aec3f9da1a643da4eb425e427e373654032d

{
  "id": "webhook-123",
  "event": "item.created",
  "timestamp": "2026-05-02T07:53:46.038Z",
  "data": {
    "itemId": "abc-456",
    "name": "Test Item"
  }
}

